title: FilmImpact.net Transition Packs Bundle TP1 v3.1.5 & TP2 v3.2
description:
FilmImpact.net Transition Pack Bundle is a great set of video transition effects for Adobe Premiere Pro. I couldn't find these on goddamn torrent sites so I'm uploading it myself. 

Beware that this is my first ever torrent upload, so please don't open fire to my chest with your fully loaded AK-47's. I scanned the installer with Kaspersky PURE 3.0. It was clean. Scan when you download it too.

Creadits goes to Team V.R

------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Bundle includes 2 packs with these effects:

-Impact Flash
-Impact Roll
-Impact Push
-Impact Blur to Color
-Impact Burn Alpha
-Impact Burn White
-Impact Blur Dissolve
-Impact Stretch
-Impact Copy Machine
-Impact Chaos

-Impact Chroma Leaks
-Impact Directional Blur
-Impact Earthquake
-Impact Glass
-Impact Radial Blur
-Impact Rays
-Impact TV Power
-Impact VHS Damage
-Impact Wipe
-Impact Zoom Blur

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Latest update changelog:

08/18/2014: Transition Pack 1 V3.1.5 and Transition Pack 2 V 3.2.3 Update 
Improved: Impact Chaos has a more natural way of handling transparency
Improved: Better exposure curve for Impact Chrome Leaks
Improved: Activation Keys can now be installed for "all users" on a single computer 
Fixed: Impact TV Power and Chroma Leaks previews could show flashes when applied as a single sided transition

For more info visit: http://www.filmimpact.net/plugins/ they sell this for 108$ :/
